Detailed Description

FM Multi-way Partitioning Gain Manager (FIFO version). In this version, vertices are inserted in FIFO manner. It is expected that the performance of FIFO manager is worse than the LIFO manager. However, the difference is not noticable in the multi-level mode compared to the flat mode.

See also:
FMKWayGainMgr2.
